{"id":311,"ayahs":[{"number":77,"arabic":"أَفَرَءَيْتَ ٱلَّذِى كَفَرَ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا وَقَالَ لَأُوتَيَنَّ مَالًۭا وَوَلَدًا","translation":"And hast thou ever considered [the kind of man] who is bent on denying the truth of Our messages and says, \"I will surely be given wealth and children\"?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2327.mp3","surahId":19,"words":[{"id":62843,"position":1,"arabic":"أَفَرَءَيْتَ","translation":"কি তুমি দেখেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/019_077_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62844,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/019_077_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62845,"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرَ","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/019_077_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62846,"position":4,"arabic":"بِـَٔايَـٰتِنَا","translation":"সঙ্গে আমাদের নিদর্শনগুলোর","audioUrl":"wbw/019_077_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62847,"position":5,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","translation":"এবং বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/019_077_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62848,"position":6,"arabic":"لَأُوتَيَنَّ","translation":"\"আমাকে অবশ্যই দেয়া হবেই","audioUrl":"wbw/019_077_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62849,"position":7,"arabic":"مَالًۭا","translation":"ধন-সম্পদ","audioUrl":"wbw/019_077_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62850,"position":8,"arabic":"وَوَلَدًا","translation":"ও সন্তান\"","audioUrl":"wbw/019_077_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62851,"position":9,"arabic":"٧٧","translation":"(৭৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":78,"arabic":"أَطَّلَعَ ٱلْغَيْبَ أَمِ ٱتَّخَذَ عِندَ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ عَهْدًۭا","translation":"Has he, perchance, attained to a realm which is beyond the reach of a created being's perception? or has he concluded a covenant with the Most Gracious?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2328.mp3","surahId":19,"words":[{"id":63588,"position":1,"arabic":"أَطَّلَعَ","translation":"কি সে অবহিত হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/01